{"tid":1037674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美委員會去年建議國會檢討《香港關係法》　駐港領事：下一份報告或更嚴厲","createTime":"2019-02-26T06:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T22:05:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":110,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"cd82022beabd0e9abf5c4cfa185f38cf1209816b","tid":1037674,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/KurtTong_eW4Sr_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FKurtTong_eW4Sr_1200x0.png&h=cf738d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國的美中經濟與安全審查委員會去年底發表的報告，建議國會指示商務部審視《香港關係法》，檢討將香港和內地視為兩個獨立關稅區的政策。無綫新聞報道，美國駐港總領事唐偉康（Kurt Tong）出席無綫節目《清心直說》時指，相信委員會下一份相關的報告，對香港的評論會更嚴厲。<br />\n<br />\n美國的美中經濟與安全審查委員會去年底發表的報告，因應香港港政府取締香港民族黨、拒絕續發工作簽證予《金融時報》編輯馬凱等事件，批評北京干預香港內部事務，違反「一國兩制」，建議國會指示商務部審視《香港關係法》，檢討將香港和內地視為兩個獨立關稅區的政策。<br />\n<br />\n無綫新聞報道，唐偉康指，去年香港發生的政治事件，顯示高度自治被削弱。香港政治上限制越來越多，無綫新聞引述唐偉康表示：「過去數年有種趨勢，尤其在2018年，側重了『一國』，令『兩制』未能發揮其最大益處。我明白香港政治氣候使內地不安，但對本港施加的壓力會衝擊香港政治生態，收窄政治空間，更令美方擔憂的是，未來這可能進一步威脅營商環境。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到下一份報告會否較上一份更嚴厲，唐偉康稱：「我相信按我們去年的評估，這說法成立，正確。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/美委員會去年建議國會檢討-香港關係法-駐港領事-下一份報告或更嚴厲/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%AA%A2%E8%A8%8E-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E6%B3%95-%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B-%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%BD%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E6%88%96%E6%9B%B4%E5%9A%B4%E5%8E%B2%2F&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfaVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=03a1d797\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%AA%A2%E8%A8%8E-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E6%B3%95-%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B-%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%BD%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E6%88%96%E6%9B%B4%E5%9A%B4%E5%8E%B2%2F&h=5233a87a\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/美委員會去年建議國會檢討-香港關係法-駐港領事-下一份報告或更嚴厲/</a>"},{"pid":"5d7e65c263aa7faba7d76f9eda693e4b156ecde5","tid":1037674,"uid":152476,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:10:49.000Z","msg":"開始放風<br />\nIt&rsquo;s coming <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b212182e39ac620a36dcdd3dea687e38436782a2","tid":1037674,"uid":141151,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:16:22.000Z","msg":"Michael Chugani<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94fc49c2e195287b96206d963264e1add8456b83","tid":1037674,"uid":107927,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:17:39.000Z","msg":"仲信一國兩制都on9"},{"pid":"ed330cebb61d37998172bef172a210829110091f","tid":1037674,"uid":37586,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"下一份報告<br />\n香港已合拼為大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf969a815b9aa7ca48a6c225588d34753246785","tid":1037674,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26849e73d08bdb56d6f23478268bdbd5d45d12ca","tid":1037674,"uid":60814,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"b212182e39ac620a36dcdd3dea687e38436782a2","tid":1037674,"uid":141151,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:16:22.000Z","msg":"Michael Chugani<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\